graph LR
    CodeFlareOp[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.4.3]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlareOp -->|manages CRD lifecycle| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlareOp -->|webhook cert rotation| CertController[cert-controller<br/>v0.10.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlareOp -->|runtime framework| Ray[Ray Framework<br/>v2.5.0<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional)
    CodeFlareOp -->|workload scheduling<br/>quota management| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.6.2<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    CodeFlareOp -.->|AppWrapper controller<br/>enabled if Kueue CRD available| AppWrapper[AppWrapper<br/>v0.12.0<br/>EMBEDDED]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    CodeFlareOp -->|reads config<br/>DSCInitialization CRD| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    CodeFlareOp -.->|sidecar injection<br/>OpenShift only| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>INTERNAL - OpenShift]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    CodeFlareOp -->|API calls<br/>resource watches| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>PLATFORM]
    CodeFlareOp -->|service mesh<br/>traffic policies| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>PLATFORM - Optional]
    CodeFlareOp -->|ingress<br/>OpenShift only| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>PLATFORM - OpenShift]
    CodeFlareOp -->|ingress<br/>Kubernetes| Ingress[Kubernetes Ingress<br/>PLATFORM - Kubernetes]

    %% Integration Points (ODH/RHOAI Ecosystem)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTEGRATION] -->|creates RayCluster<br/>via UI| CodeFlareOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>INTEGRATION] -->|auto-deploy<br/>distributed training| CodeFlareOp
    Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>INTEGRATION] -->|Ray SDK<br/>distributed compute| CodeFlareOp

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>PLATFORM] -->|scrapes metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP| CodeFlareOp

    %% User Workloads
    CodeFlareOp -->|creates & manages| RayClusterPods[Ray Cluster Pods<br/>Head + Workers<br/>USER WORKLOAD]

    %% CRD Relationships
    subgraph CRDs["Custom Resource Definitions"]
        AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2<br/>OWNED]
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1<br/>WATCHED - owned by KubeRay]
        WorkloadCR[Workload CR<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1<br/>WATCHED - owned by Kueue]
        DSCInitCR[DSCInitialization CR<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io/v1<br/>WATCHED - owned by ODH Operator]
    end

    CodeFlareOp -->|owns & reconciles| AppWrapperCR
    CodeFlareOp -->|watches & mutates| RayClusterCR
    CodeFlareOp -->|creates & watches| WorkloadCR
    CodeFlareOp -->|reads config| DSCInitCR

    KubeRay -->|provides & reconciles| RayClusterCR
    Kueue -->|provides & reconciles| WorkloadCR
    ODHOperator -->|provides| DSCInitCR

